---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Section from '../components/Section.astro';
import ExperienceItem from '../components/ExperienceItem.astro';
import EducationItem from '../components/EducationItem.astro';
import SkillsBlock from '../components/SkillsBlock.astro';
import InterestsBlock from '../components/InterestsBlock.astro';
import StreamflowIcon from '../components/icons/StreamflowIcon.astro';
import AwardItem from '../components/AwardItem.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Luka Živanović - CV" description="Engineering Manager & Full‑Stack Developer">
	<Section id="summary" title="Summary" class="mt-0">
		<p class="text-zinc-300">
			Engineering Manager and full‑stack engineer with a strong background in computer science, teaching, and Web3
			product delivery. Experienced in leading and scaling cross‑functional engineering teams, defining processes,
			and driving technical direction across frontend, backend, and blockchain systems. Proven track record of
			taking products from idea to production, mentoring and hiring engineers, and contributing hands‑on to complex
			or high‑impact parts of the stack.
		</p>
	</Section>

	<Section id="work" title="Work with me">
		<p class="text-zinc-300">
			If you’re looking for senior engineering support, to ship faster, reduce risk, or level up delivery, here are a few ways we can work together.
		</p>
		<div class="mt-6 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
			<article class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/40 p-5 transition-colors">
				<h3 class="text-lg font-medium">Integration Support</h3>
				<p class="mt-1 text-sm italic text-zinc-400">Best if: you’re integrating a third-party platform/SDK (payments, auth, web3, analytics) and want it done cleanly.</p>
				<ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-zinc-300">
					<li>In-depth technical consultation (architecture, design, implementation)</li>
					<li>End to end feature delivery (frontend, backend, integrations)</li>
					<li>UX for critical flows (onboarding, checkout/claim, errors, recoveries)</li>
					<li>Testing strategy + launch readiness</li>
					<li>Production troubleshooting and performance tuning</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-zinc-400">Outcome: a stable integration that’s easy to maintain and pleasant for users.</p>
			</article>

			<article class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/40 p-5 transition-colors">
				<h3 class="text-lg font-medium">Consulting & Advisory</h3>
				<p class="mt-1 text-sm italic text-zinc-400">Best if: you need a senior set of eyes for decisions and execution.</p>
				<ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-zinc-300">
					<li>Architecture review + actionable recommendations</li>
					<li>Product/engineering alignment (scope, tradeoffs, risk mapping)</li>
					<li>Delivery systems (quality gates, release confidence, faster iteration)</li>
					<li>Mentorship (PR reviews, pairing sessions, coaching)</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-zinc-400">Outcome: clarity and a concrete plan your team can execute.</p>
			</article>

			<article class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/40 p-5 transition-colors">
				<h3 class="text-lg font-medium">Contractor / Builder (Hands-on)</h3>
				<p class="mt-1 text-sm italic text-zinc-400">Best if: you want someone to take ownership of a scoped project and ship it.</p>
				<ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-zinc-300">
					<li>End-to-end feature delivery (frontend, backend, integrations)</li>
					<li>Dashboards, internal tooling, automation</li>
					<li>Refactors and reliability improvements (testing, CI, performance)</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-zinc-400">Outcome: shipped work with high-quality handoff.</p>
			</article>

			<article class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/40 p-5 transition-colors">
				<h3 class="text-lg font-medium">Hire Me (Full-time)</h3>
				<p class="mt-1 text-sm italic text-zinc-400">Best if: you want a product-minded engineering manager who can drive delivery and build strong teams.</p>
				<ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-zinc-300">
					<li>Execution + stakeholder alignment</li>
					<li>Strong engineering practices (reviews, testing, reliability)</li>
					<li>Team leadership, hiring, mentoring</li>
					<li>Product delivery focus (shipping outcomes, not just output)</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-zinc-400">Outcome: a leader who improves both the team and the product.</p>
			</article>
		</div>
	</Section>

	<Section id="experience" title="Experience">

		<ExperienceItem
			company="Streamflow Finance"
			locationPeriod="Remote / Belgrade · Feb. 2023 - Present"
			role="Engineering Manager, ex. Frontend IC"
			href="https://streamflow.finance"
			points={[
				'Led engineering for a multi‑chain token streaming, airdrop, and staking platform (primary focus on Solana).',
				'Managed and mentored a cross‑functional team (Frontend, Backend, Blockchain, QA) and established processes and ownership.',
				'Partnered with Product and Leadership on roadmap, scoping, delivery planning, and aligning priorities with business goals.',
				'Drove engineering quality standards, hiring, growth, and day‑to‑day technical execution.',
				'Contributed hands‑on to protocol integrations, performance, and refactors to unblock delivery.'
			]}
			achievements={[
				'Scaled the engineering team from 2 to 6+ while introducing leveling and hiring processes.',
				'Shipped Token Locks, Project Dashboards, and Multi‑chain support used by 1.3M+ users.',
				'Improved delivery predictability with planning rituals, OKRs, and cross‑team communication structures.'
			]}
		>
			<StreamflowIcon slot="icon" class="h-5 w-5" />
		</ExperienceItem>

		<ExperienceItem
			company="Microsoft"
			locationPeriod="Belgrade, Serbia · Apr. 2020 - Feb. 2023"
			role="Software Engineer"
			href="https://www.microsoft.com"
			logoSrc="/logos/microsoft.svg"
			points={[
				'Worked as a full‑stack engineer on Microsoft Word for Web, Windows, and macOS clients.',
				'Built and maintained features for the first‑party Editor plugin with emphasis on reliability, performance, accessibility, and large‑scale robustness.',
				'Delivered features end‑to‑end in collaboration with cross‑team partners from design through rollout, telemetry, and long‑term maintenance.'
			]}
		/>

		<ExperienceItem
			company="Faculty of Mathematics, University of Belgrade"
			locationPeriod="Belgrade, Serbia · Oct. 2018 - Sep. 2019"
			role="Teaching Assistant"
			href="https://www.matf.bg.ac.rs"
			logoSrc="/logos/matf.svg"
			points={[
				'Assisted in teaching undergraduate courses in informatics and programming.',
				'Led exercise classes, prepared materials and assignments, and mentored students.'
			]}
		/>

		<ExperienceItem
			company="Code by Comtrade"
			locationPeriod="Belgrade, Serbia · Feb. 2019 - Aug. 2019"
			role="Teacher"
			href="https://comtrade.com"
			logoSrc="/logos/comtrade.svg"
			points={[
				'Taught web programming and software development fundamentals to adults undergoing career change.',
				'Designed exercises and practical mini‑projects to introduce real‑world web development.'
			]}
		/>
	</Section>

	<Section id="education" title="Education">
		<ul class="space-y-2">
			<EducationItem degree="Master Studies in Informatics" institution="Faculty of Mathematics, University of Belgrade" years="2017-2022" />
			<EducationItem degree="BSc in Informatics" institution="Faculty of Mathematics, University of Belgrade" years="2014-2017" />
		</ul>
	</Section>

	<Section id="awards" title="Awards">
		<ul class="space-y-2">
			<AwardItem
				title="MatHack · 2nd place · trajectory generation using machine learning"
				details="Faculty of Mathematics, Belgrade"
				date="May 2018"
			/>
			<AwardItem
				title="Deep Web Hackathon · 2nd place · deep web website analysis"
				details="Brasidas, Belgrade"
				date="Apr. 2017"
			/>
			<AwardItem
				title="Beyond Hackathon · 2nd place (of 38 teams) · Eurobank voice assistant"
				details="Eurobank, Athens"
				date="Mar. 2017"
			/>
		</ul>
	</Section>

	<Section id="skills" title="Skills">
		<SkillsBlock
			skills="Leadership, Mentoring, Hiring, Growth/Scaling, Technical Direction, Engineering"
			technologies="TypeScript, React, Python, SQL"
			notes="Selected technologies reflecting my most recent and relevant experience."
			languages="Serbian (native), English (fluent)"
		/>
	</Section>

	<Section id="interests" title="Interests">
		<InterestsBlock text="Powerlifting, e‑skateboarding, snowboarding, wakeboarding, board games, coffee, bouldering" />
	</Section>

	<Section id="contact" title="Say hi">
		<p class="text-zinc-300">Prefer async? Reach me on any of these channels.</p>
		<div class="mt-6 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3">
			<a
				href="https://t.me/Hrimthusar"
				target="_blank"
				rel="noopener noreferrer"
				class="group flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/40 p-4 transition-colors hover:bg-zinc-900/60 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-zinc-400/50"
				aria-label="Contact on Telegram"
			>
				<span class="inline-flex h-9 w-9 aspect-square shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-sky-500/15 text-sky-400 ring-1 ring-inset ring-sky-400/20">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="h-5 w-5" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
						<path d="M9.042 12.493 8.82 16.19c.454 0 .652-.195.888-.427l2.133-2.052 4.422 3.237c.811.447 1.387.212 1.607-.75l2.91-13.645h.001c.258-1.203-.435-1.675-1.227-1.384L1.12 8.27c-1.177.457-1.16 1.113-.2 1.41l4.9 1.525L18.93 5.28c.701-.445 1.335-.199.811.246" />
					</svg>
				</span>
				<div class="min-w-0 flex flex-col">
					<span class="font-medium text-zinc-100">Telegram</span>
					<span class="truncate text-sm text-zinc-400">@Hrimthusar</span>
				</div>
			</a>
			<a
				href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/luka-%C5%BEivanovi%C4%87-1a63306b/"
				target="_blank"
				rel="noopener noreferrer"
				class="group flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/40 p-4 transition-colors hover:bg-zinc-900/60 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-zinc-400/50"
				aria-label="Open LinkedIn profile"
			>
				<span class="inline-flex h-9 w-9 aspect-square shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-blue-500/15 text-blue-400 ring-1 ring-inset ring-blue-400/20">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512" class="h-5 w-5" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
						<path d="M100.28 448H7.4V148.9h92.88zm-46.44-341C24 107 0 83 0 53.64 0 24.29 24.29 0 53.64 0c29.35 0 53.64 24.29 53.64 53.64 0 29.36-24.28 53.36-53.44 53.36zM447.9 448h-92.68V302.4c0-34.7-.7-79.1-48.2-79.1-48.2 0-55.6 37.7-55.6 76.6V448H158.8V148.9h88.9v40.8h1.3c12.4-23.5 42.6-48.2 87.7-48.2 93.8 0 111 61.8 111 142.3z"/>
					</svg>
				</span>
				<div class="min-w-0 flex flex-col">
					<span class="font-medium text-zinc-100">LinkedIn</span>
				</div>
			</a>
			<a
				href="mailto:lukazivanovic@gmail.com"
				class="group flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/40 p-4 transition-colors hover:bg-zinc-900/60 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-zinc-400/50"
				aria-label="Send email to lukazivanovic@gmail.com"
			>
				<span class="inline-flex h-9 w-9 aspect-square shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-500/15 text-emerald-400 ring-1 ring-inset ring-emerald-400/20">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="h-5 w-5" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
						<path d="M2.25 6.75A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 4.5 4.5h15a2.25 2.25 0 0 1 2.25 2.25v10.5A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 19.5 19.5h-15A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 2.25 17.25zm2.4.75 7.35 4.41L19.35 7.5zM19.5 9.3l-7.5 4.5-7.5-4.5v7.95a.75.75 0 0 0 .75.75h13.5a.75.75 0 0 0 .75-.75z"/>
					</svg>
				</span>
				<div class="min-w-0 flex flex-col">
					<span class="font-medium text-zinc-100">Email</span>
					<span class="truncate text-sm text-zinc-400">lukazivanovic@gmail.com</span>
				</div>
			</a>
		</div>
	</Section>
</BaseLayout>
